data.description: Almost 1/2 Acre Horse Property in Desired NW Area *** Bring the horses!! *** 4 Bedroom/3 Bath *** Spacious open floor plan with ceramic tile flooring in main areas & carpet in bedrooms, Ceiling fans in all rooms and mirrored closet doors *** Covered patio overlooks Small Arena and 4 Covered Horse Stalls - see your horses from the window !! ** Tack Room/Shed, mature landscaping on auto irrigation system *** Near Floyd Lamb Park for best trail riding in Town!! *** These small inexpensive Horse Properties are hard to come by and they sell fast !! ***
